La Palma is a very various Island which is also called Isla Bonita.
With our 5 Enduro Biketours you will explore the different climate an vegetation zones of the island on endless trails. Our daily shuttle brings us to the best starting points.
In the afternoon we have a small break in local tapas bars and after the ride we meet with other groups for the apres bike at the beach of Puerto Naos

With our 5 Enduro Biketours you will explore the different climate an vegetation zones of the island on endless trails. Our daily shuttle brings us to the best starting points.
In the afternoon we have a small break in local tapas bars and after the ride we meet with other groups for the apres bike at the beach of Puerto Naos
